### 淘书网API测试文件
### 使用IDEA HTTP Client测试
### 基础URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083

### ==========================================
### 用户模块测试
### ==========================================

### 1. 注册用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "小王"
}

### 2. 用户登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 从登录响应中提取token(手动复制或使用如下方式)
### 在IDEA中,登录后可以在响应中看到token,复制到下方

### 3. 获取用户信息(需要token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjEsInBob25lIjoiMTM4MDAxMzgwMDAiLCJzdWIiOiIxIiwiaWF0IjoxNzEwNzY4ODg5LCJleHAiOjE3MTA4NTUyODl9.xxxxx

### ==========================================
### 商品模块测试
### ==========================================

### 4. 创建商品(需要token,先登录获取token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/book
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java编程思想",
  "author": "Bruce Eckel",
  "publisher": "机械工业出版社",
  "isbn": "9787111213826",
  "price": 88.00,
  "stock": 10,
  "description": "Java经典书籍,适合初学者和进阶者"
}

### 5. 创建第二本商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/book
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot实战",
  "author": "Craig Walls",
  "publisher": "人民邮电出版社",
  "price": 79.00,
  "stock": 15,
  "description": "Spring Boot入门经典"
}

### 6. 查询商品列表(公开,无需token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/book/list?page=0&size=10

### 7. 搜索商品(公开)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/book/search?keyword=Java&page=0&size=10

### 8. 查询商品详情(公开)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/book/1

### 9. 更新商品(需要token,只能更新自己的商品)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/book/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 78.00,
  "stock": 20
}

### 10. 查询我的商品(需要token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/book/my
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. 删除商品(需要token,只能删除自己的商品)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/book/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ==========================================
### 测试异常情况
### ==========================================

### 12. 测试: 手机号格式错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "123",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 13. 测试: 密码太短
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "password": "123"
}

### 14. 测试: 重复注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 15. 测试: 错误的密码登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 16. 测试: 无token访问需要认证的接口
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/info

### 17. 测试: 无效token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/info
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

### ==========================================
### 完整测试流程
### ==========================================

### 步骤1: 注册新用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139999",
  "password": "test123",
  "nickname": "测试用户"
}

### 步骤2: 登录并获取token
# @name testLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139999",
  "password": "test123"
}

### 步骤3: 使用token创建商品(需要手动复制token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/book
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_FROM_STEP2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "算法导论",
  "author": "Thomas H. Cormen",
  "price": 128.00,
  "stock": 5
}

### 步骤4: 查询商品列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/book/list?page=0&size=10

### ==========================================
### H2数据库查询
### ==========================================

### 注意: H2控制台需要浏览器访问
### 访问地址: http://localhost:8083/h2-console
### JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:taoshu-db
### User: sa
### Password: (空)

### SQL查询示例:
-- SELECT * FROM user;
-- SELECT * FROM book;
